Flask is a lightweight python based web framework used to build web applications and API
its also known as micro-framework because it does not force you to any specific tool or libraries you add what you need.

Why Use it.
1.Easy to learn and minimal bilerplate
2.Flexible you decice database authentication , templates etc.
3.Good for samll to medium app,APIs and as starting point for bigger system.
4.Building Rest APIs
5.Dashboards
6.Serving machine learning models.
7.Backend apps.

